 types, photometry, reddening, binarity, and the\ngrid of absolute magnitudes. We anticipate that future measurements in Gaia-DR3\nwill improve the precision of distances to massive star-forming regions in the\nMilky Way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2019 18:00:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Aug 2019 17:38:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
