ependent And-Parallelism, report on an\nimplementation within the CiaoPP system, and provide some experimental results.\nTo our knowledge, this is the first approach to the cost analysis of parallel\nlogic programs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2019 01:20:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-01"}
